opus (4.0.2-2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Watch file added
  * debconf_config.php now protected by ucf
  * Removed support for installation with apache 1 which is no longer in sid
  * Fixed Vcs-Svn to only use a URL, not a command
  * Packaging for opus-doc now only ships the resulting PDF, not Latex
  * Cookie secrets are now generated automatically if left blank

 -- Colin Turner <c.turner@ulster.ac.uk>  Sat, 17 May 2008 23:46:49 +0100

